summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1 to 6, inclusive, Block 2, and Lots 8 to 14, inclusive, Block 6, Replat of Blocks 1, 2, 6, 7, 13, 14 and 23, North Seattle with respect to Use Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382 as amended by adding thereto a new section numbered 2-119.
